<h3 class="mb-3 mt-5">Cookies & Your Personal Data</h3>
<p>Cookies may collect personal data, such as IP addresses and browsing activities. This data can be used to personalize your experience. We handle this information securely and in compliance with data protection laws, including the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR). For more details, see our Privacy Policy.</p>
<h3 class="mb-3 mt-5">Cookie Retention Period</h3>
<p>Cookies have different lifespans. Session cookies disappear when you close your browser, while persistent cookies remain until they expire or are manually deleted. We ensure that cookies are only kept as long as necessary, typically not exceeding 2 years.</p>
